<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>账号验证邮件</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2ff;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(147, 164, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .decoration-top {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80%;
            height: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #93a4ff, #f3a6ff);
            border-radius: 15px;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .decoration-bottom {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60%;
            height: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f3a6ff, #93a4ff);
            border-radius: 15px;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header img {
            width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #6c7bff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(108, 123, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #f0f2ff 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .verify-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6c7bff, #f3a6ff);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 25px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(108, 123, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .verify-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(108, 123, 255, 0.4);
        }
        .verify-button::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        .verify-button:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: rotate(45deg) translate(50%, 50%);
        }
        .note {
            color: #7a7a9d;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #7a7a9d;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .kawaii-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .manual-link {
            color: #6c7bff;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(108, 123, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .floating-hearts {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 16px;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            color: rgba(243, 166, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .heart-1 { top: 20px; left: 20px; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .heart-2 { top: 60px; right: 30px; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .heart-3 { bottom: 40px; left: 40px; animation-delay: 1s; }
        .heart-4 { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; animation-delay: 1.5s; }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(5deg); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="decoration-top"></div>
    <div class="decoration-bottom"></div>
    <span class="floating-hearts heart-1">♥</span>
    <span class="floating-hearts heart-2">♥</span>
    <span class="floating-hearts heart-3">♥</span>
    <span class="floating-hearts heart-4">♥</span>

    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://example.com/your-logo.png" alt="Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="title">
        <span class="kawaii-icon">✨</span>
        验证您的账号
        <span class="kawaii-icon">✨</span>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>亲爱的用户：</p>
        <p>欢迎加入我们的小家庭！请点击下面的按钮验证您的账号~</p>

        <a href="https://your-website.com/verify?token=YOUR_TOKEN" class="verify-button">
            开启奇妙旅程 →
        </a>

        <p class="note">
            <span class="kawaii-icon">⏰</span> 温馨提示：此验证链接将在24小时后失效哦～<br>
            如果这不是您的操作，请忽略此邮件。
        </p>

        <p class="manual-link">
            如果按钮无法点击，请复制以下链接到浏览器中打开：<br>
            ${link}
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复 <span class="kawaii-icon">🌸</span></p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Zeeyeh Studio. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
